Visualize

piRNAs

library(ggplot2)

theme_set(theme_bw())
h<-read.table("/Users/rokofler/analysis/2021-Dere-Pele/analysis/2021-09-piRNAs/05-distribution-on-pele/raw-piRNA/line-forr.txt")
#R1 1   RT1C    1012    0.774674346272
#R1 1   RT1C    826 1.54934869254
#R1 1   RT1C    580 0.774674346272
names(h)<-c("rep","time","te","pos","pirna")
h<-subset(h,te=="PPI251")
h$time<-as.factor(h$time)

ylow=min(h$pirna)
yhigh=max(h$pirna)

p<- ggplot(h,aes(x=pos,y=pirna))+geom_segment(aes(xend=pos),yend=0)+facet_grid(time~rep)+ylim(ylow,yhigh)+ylab("piRNA abundance [pmp]")+xlab("position of piRNA (5' end)")
plot(p)

pdf(file="/Users/rokofler/analysis/2021-Dere-Pele/analysis/2021-09-piRNAs/05-distribution-on-pele/graphs/distri-pirna-onpele.pdf",width=8,height=10)
plot(p)
dev.off()
